  "Description": {
    "English": "Specialist harmonic resonators allow the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Spitter</span> to split inserted ammunition, effective manufacturing more shots from fewer materials.<br><br>Increases <span class=\"name name-stellar\">weapon clip size</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专业的谐波谐振器，允许<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲喷射器</span>分离嵌入的弹药，从而用更少的材料制造出更多的弹药。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">武器弹匣容量</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "专业的谐波谐振器，允许<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲喷射器</span>分离嵌入的弹药，从而用更少的材料制造出更多的弹药。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">武器弹匣容量</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專業的諧波諧振器，允許<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝槍</span>分離嵌入的彈藥，從而用更少的材料製造出更多的彈藥。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">武器彈匣容量</span>。"
  },
